dc_description_s: [This feature class contains the location of farmland preservation areas as designated in farmland preservation plans that have been certified by DATCP since July 1, 2009. This feature class was created by DATCP by standardizing and aggregating data submitted by counties as part of the farmland preservation plan certification process. This feature class was last updated January 2019.]
dc_creator_sm: Wisconsin Department of Agriculture, Trade and Consumer Protection
